law.history: Repealed 2007 Ky. Acts ch. 85, sec. 334, effective June 26, 2007. -- Amended 1974 Ky. Acts ch. 74, Art. V, sec. 24(1). -- Created 1956 (1st Extra. Sess.) Ky. Acts ch. 7, Art. X, sec. 16, effective September 1, 1956.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Justice Cabinet may make rules and direct proceedings.
